
Thrust Calculator 
---

*THIS IS A WORK IN PROGRESS*

Absolutely essential parts (minimum to fly a basic drone):

Frame
Motors
Propellers
Electronic Speed Controllers (ESCs)
Flight Controller
Battery (LiPo)
Battery Connector
Wiring
Radio Transmitter
Radio Receiver

---

Essential but often built-in / optional depending on setup:

Power Distribution Board (or ESC power leads)
Voltage Regulator / BEC
Gyroscope & Accelerometer (usually inside the flight controller)

---

NOT essential to just fly (optional features):

GPS Module
Telemetry
Camera / FPV system
Gimbal
Landing Gear
Prop Guards
Buzzer, LEDs
Compass, Barometer
